author: Andrew Feinberg
title: U.S. Intelligence Agencies Haven't Agreed on Any One Theory About How Coronavirus Originated
description: Though a Fox News report claimed the novel coronavirus was accidentally released from a virology lab, an U.S. Intelligence Community official tells Newsweek that America's intelligence agencies haven't come to a conclusion about the origins of the SARS-CoV-2 …
content:
America's intelligence agencies have not come to a conclusion on how the virus known as SARS-CoV-2 began spreading from China's Wuhan province, a U.S. Intelligence Community official told Newsweek on Friday.
